{"data":[{"date":"21:37 11/08","title":"Th\u1ea5y g\u00ec sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Tottenham tr\u01b0\u1edbc Newcastle?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/tot.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tottenham \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Newcastle v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-1, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd tr\u1eadn Newcastle vs Tottenham v\u00f2ng 1 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Dele Alli ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u00e0 th\u1ea7n t\u00e0i c\u1ee7a Tottenham</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Newcastle, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Dele Alli d\u00f9 m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y \u00edt ng\u00e0y nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ngay t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i trong s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4-2-3-1.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n Newcastle vs Tottenham v\u00f2ng 1 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n Newcastle vs Tottenham v\u00f2ng 1 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/Diem-nhan-Newcastle-vs-Tottenham-vong-1-Ngoai-hang-Anh-201819-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Alli l\u00e0 th\u1ea7n t\u00e0i c\u1ee7a Tottenham</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1996 l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao ch\u01a1i hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Tottenham \u1edf s\u00e2n St James' Park, anh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch nh\u1ea5t (2) b\u00ean ph\u00eda Spurs v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u1ec3n h\u00f3a th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPh\u00fat 18, Aurier th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng c\u0103ng ngang t\u1eeb bi\u00ean v\u00e0o trung l\u1ed9, Dele Alli kh\u00e9o l\u00e9o di chuy\u1ec3n tho\u00e1t ra kh\u1ecfi s\u1ef1 \u0111eo b\u00e1m t\u1eeb h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng, anh ch\u1ecdn v\u1ecb tr\u00ed thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i v\u00e0 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec7m b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi tr\u1ed1ng. B\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Alli mang v\u1ec1 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n cho Spurs.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1ed1ng k\u00ea ch\u1ec9 ra r\u1eb1ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 th\u1ea7n t\u00e0i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Tottenham ch\u01b0a thua m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn n\u00e0o \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh khi Dele Alli ghi b\u00e0n (32 tr\u1eadn, 26 th\u1eafng v\u00e0 6 h\u00f2a).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Harry Kane ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong th\u00e1ng 8</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, Harry Kane th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong th\u00e1ng 8. T\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Newcastle, ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1993 \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua 13 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp trong th\u00e1ng 8 v\u1edbi 898 ph\u00fat v\u00e0 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n 44 c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n Newcastle vs Tottenham v\u00f2ng 1 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n Newcastle vs Tottenham v\u00f2ng 1 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/Diem-nhan-Newcastle-vs-Tottenham-vong-1-Ngoai-hang-Anh-201819-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Harry Kane ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c kh\u00f4ng ghi b\u00e0n trong th\u00e1ng 8</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 l\u1eddi nguy\u1ec1n th\u00e1ng 8: \u201cT\u00f4i s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Totteham s\u1edbm h\u01a1n d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi. T\u00f4i th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong th\u00e1ng 8 v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n thay \u0111\u1ed5i \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Tottenham vs Newcastle v\u00f2ng 1 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19 Harry Kane \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c, nh\u01b0ng anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n. D\u00f9 \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n 90 ph\u00fat nh\u01b0ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 n\u1ed5i m\u1ed9t c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 2 c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00f4ng tr\u00fang khung th\u00e0nh, r\u1ea5t may cho Tottenham l\u00e0 Kane g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng song h\u1ecd v\u1eabn c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nh\u1edd hai pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Jan Vertonghen v\u00e0 Dele Alli.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Jan Vertonghen v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea3m x\u00fac tr\u00e1i chi\u1ec1u</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Jan Vertonghen \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua nh\u1eefng cung b\u1eadc c\u1ea3m x\u00fac kh\u00e1c nhau trong chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Newcastle. Ngay ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 8, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Tottenham v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean sau c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c \u1edf c\u1ef1 ly g\u1ea7n.\u00a0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jan Vertonghen tu vui mung, that vong cho den lo lang\" title=\"Jan Vertonghen t\u1eeb vui m\u1eebng, th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng cho \u0111\u1ebfn lo l\u1eafng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/213405-jan.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Jan Vertonghen t\u1eeb vui m\u1eebng, th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng cho \u0111\u1ebfn lo l\u1eafng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSau 163 tr\u1eadn, Vertonghen m\u1edbi l\u1ea1i ghi b\u00e0n \u1edf gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ch\u1ec9 2 ph\u00fat sau \u0111\u00f3 anh m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng gi\u00fap Joselu g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a cho Newcastle.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 v\u00e0 Sanchez \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 b\u00ean ph\u00eda Newcastle d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Hugo Lloris \u1edf c\u1ef1 ly g\u1ea7n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPh\u00fat 85, Jan Vertonghen l\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eafc \u0111\u1ebfn m\u00ecnh. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00e0o s\u00e2n thay ng\u01b0\u1eddi Salomon Rondon c\u00f3 c\u00fa s\u00fat r\u1ea5t c\u0103ng, b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1eadp ch\u00e2n Vertonghen \u0111\u1ed5i h\u01b0\u1edbng khi\u1ebfn th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Lloris b\u00f3 tay, r\u1ea5t may l\u00e0 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1eadp x\u00e0 ngang bay ra ngo\u00e0i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nN\u1ebfu b\u00f3ng \u0111i v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Vertonghen s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed3 v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 Spurs s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1nh r\u01a1i 2 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c tra t\u1ea5n t\u00e2m l\u00fd k\u00e9o d\u00e0i, anh ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1edf ph\u00e0o khi ti\u1ebfng c\u00f2i k\u1ebft th\u00fac tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u vang l\u00ean.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Pochettino c\u00f9ng Tottenham kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau 15 n\u0103m m\u1edbi c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung n\u00e0o \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a H\u00e8, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 Tottenham c\u1ee7a Pochettino. Kinh ph\u00ed x\u00e2y SV\u0110 m\u1edbi qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 bu\u1ed9c Spurs ph\u1ea3i th\u1eaft ch\u1eb7t chi ti\u00eau.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pochettino cung Tottenham co 3 diem dau tien o Ngoai hang Anh 2018/19\" title=\"Pochettino c\u00f9ng Tottenham c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/tot.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Pochettino c\u00f9ng Tottenham c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nR\u1ea5t may v\u1edbi Tottenham l\u00e0 d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung n\u00e0o, nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd c\u0169ng gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh nh\u01b0 Harry Kane, Dele Alli, Hugo Lloris hay Christian Eriksen.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Newcastle kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng, b\u1edfi \u201cCh\u00edch ch\u00f2e\u201d ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 v\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 1 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong 8 l\u1ea7n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i St James' Park. Tuy nhi\u00ean, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Pochettino \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t kh\u00f3 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTottenham v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 2-1 sau 18 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u, trong th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i Newcastle \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng nh\u01b0ng Spurs \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Pochettino \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf t\u00fai 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 Tottenham g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch song m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trong Top 4 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 h\u1ecd to\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>L\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Newcastle kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i so v\u1edbi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018, Newcastle \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 6 t\u00e2n binh, bao g\u1ed3m th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Dubravka (Sparta Prague), trung v\u1ec7 Fabian Schar (Deportivo), ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ki Sung-Yueng (Swansea), Kenedy (Chelsea), ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Yoshinori Muto (Mainz) v\u00e0 Salomon Rondon (West Brom).<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Newcastle khong cho thay su thay doi so voi mua giai truoc\" title=\"Newcastle kh\u00f4ng cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i so v\u1edbi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/new-7.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Newcastle kh\u00f4ng cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i so v\u1edbi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Rafa Benitez kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i so v\u1edbi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc, song nh\u1eefng g\u00ec di\u1ec5n ra \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Tottenham kh\u00f4ng cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a \u201cCh\u00edch ch\u00f2e\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNewcastle v\u1eabn d\u1ef1a nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng t\u1ea1t b\u00f3ng t\u1eeb hai bi\u00ean v\u00e0 khai th\u00e1c nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh, h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng b\u00e0i b\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn khung th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n h\u01a1n nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u00f9ng vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1edbn trong l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a Newcastle \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng. S\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecd m\u01a1 \u0111\u1ebfn v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 r\u00f5 n\u00e9t.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2261","checkdouble":"194276"},{"date":"22:17 11/08","title":"H\u1ecd n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn Newcastle 1-2 Tottenham?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/ho-noi-gi-sau-tran-newcastle-12-tottenham.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Mauricio Pochettino ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Newcastle vs Tottenham, \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. B\u00ean kia chi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn, Rafa Benitez cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng c\u00f3 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Pochettino \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao tinh th\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nD\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung n\u00e0o \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 v\u00e0 c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 t\u1eadp trung c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u, song Tottenham \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Newcastle v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-1. Spurs \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mauricio Pochettino ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Newcastle vs Tottenham h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Mauricio Pochettino ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Newcastle vs Tottenham h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/ho-noi-gi-sau-tran-newcastle-12-tottenham.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Pochettino \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao tinh th\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nMauricio Pochettino ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Newcastle vs Tottenham, \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cC\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i, \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 di\u1ec5n ra thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng. H\u00f4m nay, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb s\u1ef1 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. T\u00f4i h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Newcastle\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cDele Alli l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khen ng\u1ee3i, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y d\u00f9 m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau qu\u00e3ng ngh\u1ec9 \u1edf World Cup 2018 nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e3 duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1 r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t. H\u00f4m nay, m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Alli th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cC\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c t\u1ed1t ngay t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00fap ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf, sau \u0111\u00f3 Tottenham \u0111\u00e3 ki\u00ean c\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh qu\u1ea3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Rafael Benitez cho r\u1eb1ng Newcastle x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng c\u00f3 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Pochettino t\u1ecf ra vui m\u1eebng v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00ec Rafa Benitez c\u1ee7a Newcastle l\u1ea1i t\u1ecf ra ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i, \u00f4ng cho r\u1eb1ng \u201cCh\u00edch ch\u00f2e\u201d x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng c\u00f3 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Newcastle khong cho thay su thay doi so voi mua giai truoc\" title=\"Newcastle kh\u00f4ng cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i so v\u1edbi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/new-7.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Benitez cho r\u1eb1ng Newcastle x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng c\u00f3 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. Newcaste \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t sau khi nh\u1eadn b\u00e0n thua, ngay c\u1ea3 khi b\u1ecb d\u1eabn 2-1 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. Tottenham gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n v\u00ec h\u1ecd may m\u1eafn h\u01a1n ch\u00fang t\u00f4i\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cNewcaste \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a, nh\u01b0ng x\u00e0 ngang l\u1ea1i t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Salomon Rondon, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i k\u00e9m may m\u1eafn h\u01a1n Tottenham \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cC\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf m\u00ecnh, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi, t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng v\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2260","checkdouble":"194277"},{"date":"21:56 11/08","title":"Real Madrid 3-1 AC Milan: M\u00e0n ch\u1ea1y \u0111\u00e0 ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o cho Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/real-madrid-vs-ac-milan-tran-dau-giao-huu-clb-he-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u00e0n ra qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a HLV Sarri \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n, d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Huddersfield vs Chelsea t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1 Premier League.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng con s\u1ed1 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt Huddersfield vs Chelsea<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">802 &ndash; Chelsea l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee9 3 trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed Premier League gi\u00e0nh h\u01a1n 800 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch (802), v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Arsenal (800) v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n k\u00e9m Man United (902).<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea 3-0 Huddersfield\" title=\"Chelsea 3-0 Huddersfield\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-man-ra-quan-suon-se-cua-chelsea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea 3-0 Huddersfield</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">3 &ndash; Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3 sao ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay \u0111\u00e1nh d\u1ea5u tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Chelsea, k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb th\u1eddi Felipe Scolari v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2008 (th\u1eafng 4-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Portmouth).<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">6 &ndash; Kh\u00f4ng ai s\u1edf h\u1eefu nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u01b0 Eden Hazard, v\u1edbi 6/6 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng (t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 100%). Kinh ho\u00e0ng hoan, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 ch\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 14 ph\u00fat trong tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">109 &ndash; Eden Hazard \u0111\u00e3 g\u00f3p d\u1ea5u gi\u00e0y v\u00e0o 109 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong 209 tr\u1eadn Premier League. Trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 69 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 40 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o.</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Hazard vs Huddersfield\" title=\"Hazard vs Huddersfield\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/12/haz.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Huddersfield vs Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">94 &ndash; \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 % chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n binh Jorginho trong tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, m\u1ed9t con s\u1ed1 r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">1 &ndash; Trong 11 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng s\u00fat ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n t\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1edbi nay, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Jorginho ch\u1ec9 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u0111\u00fang 1 l\u1ea7n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">8 &ndash; Jorginho l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 th\u1ee9 8 trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed Premier League \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u00fat ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n trong tr\u1eadn ra m\u1eaft.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">1 &ndash; Kante c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi Premier League. Trong 3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, m\u1ed7i mua Kante \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9 ghi v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_278917\" style=\"width:100%;\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&amp;vid=premierleague/2018/08/11/huddersfield-chelsea.mp4&amp;autoplay=false\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" oallowfullscreen=\"\" msallowfullscreen=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"340\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-man-ra-quan-suon-se-cua-chelsea-172-194281.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-man-ra-quan-suon-se-cua-chelsea.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-man-ra-quan-suon-se-cua-chelsea-172-194281.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau m\u00e0n ra qu\u00e2n su\u00f4n s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Chelsea</span><br>\r\nTr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean Premier League c\u1ee7a Sarri \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ebft th\u00fac thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Huddersfield vs Chelsea 0-3.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/huddersfield-vs-chelsea-ngoai-hang-anh-1182018-372-194264.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/ket-qua-huddersfield-vs-chelsea-1182018.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/huddersfield-vs-chelsea-ngoai-hang-anh-1182018-372-194264.html\">Huddersfield 0-3 Chelsea (KT): Sarri-ball ra m\u1eaft t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng \u1edf Premier League</span><br>\r\nD\u00f9 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i ch\u01b0a th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 nhuy\u1ec5n do c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u thu v\u1eeba ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn tri\u1ebft l\u00fd c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y m\u1edbi ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bao l\u00e2u, The Blues v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i kh\u00e1 \u0111\u1eadm tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch t\u1ea1i...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2259","checkdouble":"194278"},{"date":"23:29 11/08","title":"D\u01b0 \u00e2m Newcastle 1-2 Tottenham: Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/du-am-newcastle-12-tottenham-chien-thang-cua-hang-thu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tottenham \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19 b\u1eb1ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Newcastle. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Newcastle vs Tottenham, chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Spurs mang \u0111\u1eadm d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng Tottenham ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Newcastle, HLV Pochettino \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4-2-3-1 v\u1edbi Harry Kane \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung phong, ph\u00eda sau l\u00e0 b\u1ed9 ba Lucas Moura, Christian Eriksen v\u00e0 Dele Alli.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m Newcastle vs Tottenham Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m Newcastle vs Tottenham Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/Du-am-Newcastle-vs-Tottenham-Chien-thang-cua-hang-thu-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>H\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng Tottenham thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc Newcastle</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u0111ang c\u00f3 trong tay, song h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Spurs c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u00ean s\u00e2n St James' Park. Nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Tottenham kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 li\u00ean k\u1ebft c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft, trung phong Harry Kane kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cung c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ee7 b\u00f3ng t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng v\u1ec7 tinh xung quanh.&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a Spurs ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ebfn sau nh\u1eefng qu\u1ea3 treo b\u00f3ng t\u1eeb bi\u00ean v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m ho\u1eb7c nh\u1eefng pha \u0111\u1ed9t ph\u00e1 c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n thay v\u00ec nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p nhu\u1ea7n nhuy\u1ec5n v\u00e0 b\u00e0i b\u1ea3n.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nB\u1ed9 t\u1ee9 tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Tottenham g\u1ed3m Harry Kane, Lucas Moura, Christian Eriksen v\u00e0 Dele Alli ch\u1ec9 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m 7 l\u1ea7n v\u00e0 3 trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 \u0111i tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch, qu\u00e1 khi\u00eam t\u1ed1n so v\u1edbi \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrung phong Harry Kane l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Tottenham. D\u00f9 \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n 90 ph\u00fat nh\u01b0ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch n\u00e0o, Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi World Cup 2018 ch\u1ec9 tung ra 2 c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m ra ngo\u00e0i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Harry Kane tiep tuc khong ghi ban trong thang 8\" title=\"Harry Kane ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c kh\u00f4ng ghi b\u00e0n trong th\u00e1ng 8\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/Diem-nhan-Newcastle-vs-Tottenham-vong-1-Ngoai-hang-Anh-201819-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Harry Kane ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c kh\u00f4ng ghi b\u00e0n trong th\u00e1ng 8</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea1ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t sau g\u1ea7n 3 tu\u1ea7n ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i, v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa Kane l\u1ea1i ch\u01a1i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng trong th\u00e1ng 8. &ldquo;T\u1ecbt ng\u00f2i&rdquo; tr\u01b0\u1edbc Newcastle, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua 14 tr\u1eadn v\u1edbi 988 ph\u00fat v\u00e0 46 c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n trong th\u00e1ng 8.&nbsp; &nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLucas Moura ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng kh\u00e1 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c, song hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u. Nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n anh ch\u1ec9 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch, c\u1ef1u sao PSG kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00e0o cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. V\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ee9c, Moura ph\u1ea3i nh\u01b0\u1eddng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed cho Dembele \u1edf ph\u00fat 68.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nDele Alli v\u00e0 Christian Eriksen thi \u0111\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 h\u01a1n, nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00f2n vai. Alli ngo\u00e0i b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e2ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 l\u00ean 2-1 th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u, Eriksen kh\u00f4ng ph\u00e1t huy \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u00fat xa c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ecdc khe s\u1eafc l\u1eb9m m\u1edf ra c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede ph\u00eda d\u01b0\u1edbi b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m Moussa Sissoko v\u00e0 Eric Dier c\u0169ng g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p g\u00ec cho m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng. Nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00e0o s\u00e2n thay ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u01b0 Dembele hay Son Heung-Min c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea1o ra c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i hay c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0o.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng Tottenham thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u00ec h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd l\u1ea1i g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 \u1edf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng. Ch\u00ednh phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn sau l\u00e0 l\u00fd do gi\u00fap Spurs c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Newcastle.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jan Vertonghen mo ty so tu rat som\" title=\"Jan Vertonghen m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 t\u1eeb r\u1ea5t s\u1edbm\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/232537-jan.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h2>Jan Vertonghen m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 t\u1eeb r\u1ea5t s\u1edbm</h2>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNgay ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 8, b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i trung v\u1ec7 Davinson Sanchez v\u00e0 Jan Vertonghen \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. T\u1eeb c\u00fa treo b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Christian Eriksen, Sanchez \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ec3 Vertonghen d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1eadn th\u00e0nh mang v\u1ec1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau 161 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh trung v\u1ec7 Jan Vertonghen m\u1edbi l\u1ea1i ghi b\u00e0n, l\u1ea7n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t m\u00e0 anh l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng \u1edf Premier League l\u00e0 \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Swansea v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 3 n\u0103m 2013. C\u00f2n v\u1edbi Davinson Sanchez, anh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 tung ra nh\u1eefng pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t b\u00ean ph\u00eda Tottenham, anh c\u00f3 3 pha h\u00e3m th\u00e0nh, b\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a Harry Kane v\u00e0 Christian Eriksen c\u1ed9ng l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sanchez dut diem nhieu nhat ben phia Tottenham\" title=\"Sanchez d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t b\u00ean ph\u00eda Tottenham\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/chez.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Sanchez d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t b\u00ean ph\u00eda Tottenham</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 2 c\u1ee7a Tottenham, ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng l\u00e0 Dele Alli nh\u01b0ng h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n \u0111\u1eadm n\u00e9t. Theo \u0111\u00f3, ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n qu\u1ea3 t\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng l\u00e0 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i Serge Aurier. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m nh\u1eefng c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f3 nh\u1ea5t, nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Alli ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/diem-nhan-tottenham-172-194276.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/tot.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/diem-nhan-tottenham-172-194276.html\">Th\u1ea5y g\u00ec sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Tottenham tr\u01b0\u1edbc Newcastle?</span><br>\r\nTottenham \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Newcastle v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-1, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd tr\u1eadn Newcastle vs Tottenham v\u00f2ng 1 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19.</div>\r\n</div>\r\nBen Davies d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng tham gia v\u00e0o b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0o, song c\u0169ng cho th\u1ea5y kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi 1 l\u1ea7n d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 2 l\u1ea7n t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Hang thu dem ve chien thang cho Tottenham truoc Newcastle\" title=\"H\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0111em v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho Tottenham tr\u01b0\u1edbc Newcastle\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/thu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>H\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0111em v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho Tottenham tr\u01b0\u1edbc Newcastle</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTottenham \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t, m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 g\u00f3p d\u1ea5u gi\u00e0y v\u00e0o r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Tottenham. V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec di\u1ec5n ra \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Newcastle, \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2258","checkdouble":"194280"},{"date":"23:38 11/08","title":"Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau m\u00e0n ra qu\u00e2n su\u00f4n s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Chelsea","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-man-ra-quan-suon-se-cua-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean Premier League c\u1ee7a Sarri \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ebft th\u00fac thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Huddersfield vs Chelsea 0-3.\r\n</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Kante v\u00e0 vai tr\u00f2 l\u1ea1 l\u1eabm<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">So s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa \u0111\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea3o \u1edf m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Chelsea d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Sarri \u0111\u00e3 chuy\u1ec3n s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 th\u00e0nh 4-3-3 v\u1edbi phong c\u00e1ch chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt kh\u00e1c h\u1eb3n. T\u00e2n thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia mu\u1ed1n t\u1ea1o ra l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i quy\u1ebfn r\u0169, v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3ng \u0111inh Jorginho \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 m\u1ecf neo. B\u1edfi v\u1eady, Kante thay v\u00ec ch\u01a1i gi\u0103ng ngang v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea9y l\u00ean cao h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu Barkley g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, th\u00ec Kante \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 t\u1ef1 do b\u00ean tr\u1ee5c ph\u1ea3i. \u1ede \u0111\u00e2y, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n d\u00e2ng l\u00ean tham gia th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. Trong m\u1ed9t pha b\u00f3ng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, N&rsquo;Golo Kante \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u00fang l\u00fac \u0111\u00fang ch\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 cho The Blues, t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 t\u1ea1o ra th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng su\u00f4n s\u1ebb cho \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 Chelsea c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh tr\u01a1n tru h\u01a1n n\u1eefa, Kante c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh v\u1ec1 l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1nh l\u1edbn. Xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc th\u00f4i l\u00e0 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7, HLV Sarri c\u1ea7n nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed3ng b\u1ed9 ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o v\u1edbi &ldquo;b\u1ed9 n\u00e3o&rdquo; Jorginho, \u0111\u1ec3 Chelsea ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Huddersfield vs Chelsea 0-3 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Huddersfield vs Chelsea 0-3 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/Nhung-diem-nhan-tran-dau-Huddersfield-vs-Chelsea-0-3-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Kante m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 cho Chelsea kh\u00e1 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nJorginho l\u00e0 h\u1ea1t nh\u00e2n tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 v\u1eady, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. V\u1edbi vai tr\u00f2 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ph\u00e1t \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, Jorginho l\u1ea1i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t so v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, hi\u1ebfm khi t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n mang t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn cao.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 l\u1ebd m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n k\u00e9m s\u1eafc n\u00e0y, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p v\u1edbi Jorginho, Kante ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay c\u0169ng ch\u01b0a h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 nhi\u1ec1u cho anh. Tuy v\u1eady, \u0111\u00e2y m\u1edbi l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a bom t\u1ea5n 57 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u1edf Premier League, v\u00e0 c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ec3 mong ch\u1edd ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Quan tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n, Jorginho \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i tin t\u01b0\u1edfng giao tr\u1ecdng tr\u00e1ch tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n, trong b\u00e0n n\u00e2ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 l\u00ean 2-0 cho Chelsea.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jorginho cung co man chao hang tuong doi thanh cong\" title=\"Jorginho c\u0169ng c\u00f3 m\u00e0n ch\u00e0o h\u00e0ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/jorginho.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Jorginho c\u0169ng c\u00f3 m\u00e0n ch\u00e0o h\u00e0ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h2>M\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft c\u1ee7a Kepa<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 bom t\u1ea5n Kepa Arrizabalaga trong m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y, b\u1edfi s\u1ee9c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Huddersfield l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf. Tuy nhi\u00ean, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y r\u00f5 s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n tr\u1ebb tu\u1ed5i, d\u00f9 nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y qua anh ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecbu v\u00f4 s\u1ed1 \u00e1p l\u1ef1c v\u1ec1 m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 71 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. \u0110\u1ec3 nh\u1edb r\u1eb1ng, Kepa v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp c\u00f9ng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 9/8, m\u1edbi th\u1ea5y \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1ng kh\u00edch l\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ee9c n\u00e0o.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong s\u1ed1 \u00edt nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c, c\u1ef1u th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Bilbao \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0 g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi cho \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0. C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3, anh c\u0169ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, d\u00f9 v\u1eabn kh\u00e1 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng pha pressing c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. M\u1ed9t m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, \u0111em l\u1ea1i hy v\u1ecdng thay th\u1ebf Thibaut Courtois.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kepa vs Huddersfield\" title=\"Kepa vs Huddersfield\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/kepa.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Kepa kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Huddersfield</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h2>Chelsea v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-0 v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a n\u00f3i l\u00ean qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u, d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e2y th\u1ef1c ch\u1ea5t l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 tr\u00ean c\u1ea3 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi Maurizio Sarri. Nh\u00ecn chung, Chelsea \u1edf hi\u1ec7p 2 \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u, so v\u1edbi hi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o trong v\u00e0i th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m. Tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a Chelsea qu\u00e1 thi\u1ebfu s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o, trong khi Morata m\u1ea5t h\u00fat \u1edf h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea 3-0 Huddersfield\" title=\"Chelsea 3-0 Huddersfield\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/chelsea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Huddersfield vs Chelsea 0-3</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ph\u1ea3i n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng, Huddersfield qu\u00e1 y\u1ebfu khi kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Chelsea, v\u00e0 r\u1ed3i h\u1ecd d\u00ednh \u0111\u00f2n tr\u1eebng ph\u1ea1t. Nh\u1eefng pha t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a The Blues, ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng theo b\u00e0i v\u1edf g\u00ec, n\u00f3i l\u00ean s\u1ef1 thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i l\u1edbn v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 \u1edf trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. \u0110\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn, s\u1ef1 ch\u1eadm ch\u1ea1p trong tri\u1ec3n khai b\u00f3ng s\u1ebd l\u00e0m h\u1ea1i th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Sarri.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u1eabu sao, \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Chelsea t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng, v\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd c\u00f2n ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n n\u1eefa. Sau nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Huddersfield vs Chelsea, HLV Sarri c\u1ea7n t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i nhanh nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3. \u1ede v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u sau, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea1i gia \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y &ndash; Arsenal.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_278917\" style=\"width:100%;\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&amp;vid=premierleague/2018/08/11/huddersfield-chelsea.mp4&amp;autoplay=false\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" oallowfullscreen=\"\" msallowfullscreen=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"340\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/huddersfield-vs-chelsea-ngoai-hang-anh-1182018-372-194264.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/ket-qua-huddersfield-vs-chelsea-1182018.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/huddersfield-vs-chelsea-ngoai-hang-anh-1182018-372-194264.html\">Huddersfield 0-3 Chelsea (KT): Sarri-ball ra m\u1eaft t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng \u1edf Premier League</span><br>\r\nD\u00f9 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i ch\u01b0a th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 nhuy\u1ec5n do c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u thu v\u1eeba ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn tri\u1ebft l\u00fd c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y m\u1edbi ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bao l\u00e2u, The Blues v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i kh\u00e1 \u0111\u1eadm tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch t\u1ea1i...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/ket-qua-huddersfield-vs-chelsea-1182018-172-194267.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/ket-qua-huddersfield-vs-chelsea-1182018.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/ket-qua-huddersfield-vs-chelsea-1182018-172-194267.html\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Huddersfield vs Chelsea tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng 1 Premier League 2018/19</span><br>\r\nChuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt chi ti\u1ebft k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Huddersfield vs Chelsea tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng 1 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19 h\u00f4m nay. Th\u00f4ng tin k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2257","checkdouble":"194281"},{"date":"00:10 12/08","title":"Nh\u1eefng con s\u1ed1 bi\u1ebft n\u00f3i sau tr\u1eadn Huddersfield vs Chelsea","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/nhung-con-so-biet-noi-sau-tran-huddersfield-vs-chelsea.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u00e0n ra qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a HLV Sarri \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n, d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Huddersfield vs Chelsea t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1 Premier League.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng con s\u1ed1 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt Huddersfield vs Chelsea<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">802 &ndash; Chelsea l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee9 3 trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed Premier League gi\u00e0nh h\u01a1n 800 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch (802), v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Arsenal (800) v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n k\u00e9m Man United (902).<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea 3-0 Huddersfield\" title=\"Chelsea 3-0 Huddersfield\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-man-ra-quan-suon-se-cua-chelsea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea 3-0 Huddersfield</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">3 &ndash; Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3 sao ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay \u0111\u00e1nh d\u1ea5u tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Chelsea, k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb th\u1eddi Felipe Scolari v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2008 (th\u1eafng 4-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Portmouth).<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">6 &ndash; Kh\u00f4ng ai s\u1edf h\u1eefu nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u01b0 Eden Hazard, v\u1edbi 6/6 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng (t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 100%). Kinh ho\u00e0ng hoan, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 ch\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 14 ph\u00fat trong tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">109 &ndash; Eden Hazard \u0111\u00e3 g\u00f3p d\u1ea5u gi\u00e0y v\u00e0o 109 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong 209 tr\u1eadn Premier League. Trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 69 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 40 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o.</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Hazard vs Huddersfield\" title=\"Hazard vs Huddersfield\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/12/haz.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Huddersfield vs Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">94 &ndash; \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 % chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n binh Jorginho trong tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, m\u1ed9t con s\u1ed1 r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">1 &ndash; Trong 11 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng s\u00fat ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n t\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1edbi nay, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Jorginho ch\u1ec9 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u0111\u00fang 1 l\u1ea7n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">8 &ndash; Jorginho l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 th\u1ee9 8 trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed Premier League \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u00fat ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n trong tr\u1eadn ra m\u1eaft.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">1 &ndash; Kante c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi Premier League. Trong 3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, m\u1ed7i mua Kante \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9 ghi v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_278917\" style=\"width:100%;\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&amp;vid=premierleague/2018/08/11/huddersfield-chelsea.mp4&amp;autoplay=false\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" oallowfullscreen=\"\" msallowfullscreen=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"340\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-man-ra-quan-suon-se-cua-chelsea-172-194281.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-man-ra-quan-suon-se-cua-chelsea.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-man-ra-quan-suon-se-cua-chelsea-172-194281.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau m\u00e0n ra qu\u00e2n su\u00f4n s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Chelsea</span><br>\r\nTr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean Premier League c\u1ee7a Sarri \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ebft th\u00fac thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Huddersfield vs Chelsea 0-3.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/huddersfield-vs-chelsea-ngoai-hang-anh-1182018-372-194264.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/ket-qua-huddersfield-vs-chelsea-1182018.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/huddersfield-vs-chelsea-ngoai-hang-anh-1182018-372-194264.html\">Huddersfield 0-3 Chelsea (KT): Sarri-ball ra m\u1eaft t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng \u1edf Premier League</span><br>\r\nD\u00f9 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i ch\u01b0a th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 nhuy\u1ec5n do c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u thu v\u1eeba ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn tri\u1ebft l\u00fd c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y m\u1edbi ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bao l\u00e2u, The Blues v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i kh\u00e1 \u0111\u1eadm tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch t\u1ea1i...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2256","checkdouble":"194282"},{"date":"00:47 12/08","title":"H\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Hudderfield, t\u00e2n HLV Sarri d\u00e0nh l\u1eddi khen cho m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i t\u00ean","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/ha-guc-hudderfield-tan-hlv-sarri-danh-loi-khen-cho-mot-cai-ten.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u00f9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 14 ph\u00fat, nh\u01b0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Eden Hazard \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng v\u1edbi 1 pha ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn HLV Sarri ca ng\u1ee3i Hazard sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nSarri h\u1ebft l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a h\u00e8 m\u1ecfi m\u1ec7t v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch World Cup, c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Eden Hazard l\u00fac n\u00e0y v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea1ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do ng\u00f4i sao tuy\u1ec3n B\u1ec9 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tung v\u00e0o s\u00e2n t\u1eeb b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Huddsfield.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t pha ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o r\u1ea5t thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ec3 Pedro ghi b\u00e0n \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-0. Ch\u01b0a h\u1ebft, Hazard \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn 6 pha qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 trong v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n h\u01a1n 10 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u, m\u1ed9t con s\u1ed1 qu\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, HLV Sarri cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n copy c\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a Napoli v\u00e0o \u0111\u00e2y, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng m\u1ed9t Chelsea ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t. T\u00f4i c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng l\u1edbn v\u1edbi c\u00e1 t\u00ednh c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, t\u00f4i c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i h\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng kh\u00e1 may m\u1eafn, b\u1edfi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. To\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n trong th\u00e1ng, sau \u0111\u00f3 m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 s\u1ebd kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u1edbi k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 \u0110T qu\u1ed1c gia. T\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng Chelsea s\u1ebd l\u00e0m quen v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n ngay trong th\u00e1ng T\u00e1m.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sarri ca ng\u1ee3i Hazard trong tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Huddersfield\" title=\"Hazard vs Huddersfield\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/12/haz.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Sarri ca ng\u1ee3i Hazard trong tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Huddersfield</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;C\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m, c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 v\u00e0 g\u00e2y \u00e1p l\u1ef1c t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea9y cao t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 l\u00ean b\u00f3ng, v\u00e0 c\u1ea7n l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n nh\u01b0 trong hi\u1ec7p 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 Eden Hazard v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n 90 ph\u00fat. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp v\u00e0 t\u00edch l\u0169y th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;\u00dd t\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i l\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u00e0o s\u00e2n trong kho\u1ea3ng 15-20 ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, khi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 m\u1ecfi m\u1ec7t. T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t vui m\u1eebng v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y. \u1ede hi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, v\u00e0 n\u1ebfu nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 - b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec3u l\u1ea7m \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng&quot; - HLV&nbsp;Sarri ca ng\u1ee3i Hazard.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i l\u1edbn trong kho\u1ea3ng 15 ph\u00fat v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i thi\u00ean v\u1ec1 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. May m\u1eafn cho ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 trong hi\u1ec7p 2, Huddersfield \u0111\u00e3 m\u1ec7t v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 gia t\u0103ng s\u1ee9c \u00e9p.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_278917\" style=\"width:100%;\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&amp;vid=premierleague/2018/08/11/huddersfield-chelsea.mp4&amp;autoplay=false\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" oallowfullscreen=\"\" msallowfullscreen=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"340\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhung-con-so-biet-noi-sau-tran-huddersfield-vs-chelsea-172-194282.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/nhung-con-so-biet-noi-sau-tran-huddersfield-vs-chelsea.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhung-con-so-biet-noi-sau-tran-huddersfield-vs-chelsea-172-194282.html\">Nh\u1eefng con s\u1ed1 bi\u1ebft n\u00f3i sau tr\u1eadn Huddersfield vs Chelsea</span><br>\r\nM\u00e0n ra qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a HLV Sarri \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n, d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Huddersfield vs Chelsea t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1 Premier League.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-man-ra-quan-suon-se-cua-chelsea-172-194281.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-man-ra-quan-suon-se-cua-chelsea.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-man-ra-quan-suon-se-cua-chelsea-172-194281.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau m\u00e0n ra qu\u00e2n su\u00f4n s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Chelsea</span><br>\r\nTr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean Premier League c\u1ee7a Sarri \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ebft th\u00fac thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Huddersfield vs Chelsea 0-3.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2255","checkdouble":"194283"},{"date":"01:24 12/08","title":"\"Bom t\u1ea5n\" c\u1ee7a Liverpool xo\u00e1y s\u00e2u v\u00e0o n\u1ed7i \u0111au c\u1ee7a MU","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/20/bom-tan-cua-liverpool-xoay-sau-vao-noi-dau-cua-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Fabinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh ch\u01b0a khi n\u00e0o nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c t\u1eeb Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf khi c\u00f2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho Monaco.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">MU ch\u01b0a g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb mua Fabinho</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong th\u1eddi gian ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Fabinho c\u00f2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho Monaco, nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh MU mu\u1ed1n mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993. Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 \u0111a n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a anh v\u1ec1 Old Trafford.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Fabinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Fabinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/20/bom-tan-cua-liverpool-xoay-sau-vao-noi-dau-cua-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Fabinho ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 ch\u01b0a nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1eeb MU</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u00e1o ch\u00ed Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh M.U \u0111\u00e3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Fabinho \u0111\u1ebfn Monaco, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb cao nh\u1ea5t tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 36 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, t\u00e2n binh c\u1ee7a Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nFabinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh ch\u01b0a khi n\u00e0o nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c t\u1eeb Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf khi c\u00f2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho Monaco.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cKhi c\u00f2n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Monaco, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 nghe nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n M.U mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 m\u00ecnh, nh\u01b0ng ch\u01b0a khi n\u00e0o t\u00f4i nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c t\u1eeb h\u1ecd c\u1ea3. Monaco c\u0169ng ch\u01b0a nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1eeb M.U, b\u1edfi n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o v\u1edbi t\u00f4i\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cC\u00f3 l\u1ebd h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ho\u1eb7c c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb th\u1ea5p, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn Monaco nhanh ch\u00f3ng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i. Khi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1eeb Liverpool t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 nhanh ch\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ec3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1edbi Anfield\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Fabinho tin Liverpool c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh m\u00f9a t\u1edbi</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Jurgen Klopp \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea5p 175 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Fabinho, Alisson, Naby Keita v\u00e0 Xherdan Shaqiri, v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Fabinho tin Liverpool c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh m\u00f9a t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alisson Fabinho Keita\" title=\"Alisson Fabinho Keita\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/25/nhan-dinh-liverpool-truoc-them-nha-201819-da-den-luc-nghi-ve-ngai-vang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Fabinho tin Liverpool c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea1nh tranh c\u1ee7a Liverpool s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3. T\u00f4i tin \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cNgo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t, lu\u00f4n c\u00f3 kho\u1ea3ng 5 \u0111\u1ebfn 6 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ea1nh tranh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. Liverpool l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u0103ng quang, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i duy tr\u00ec s\u1ef1 t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2254","checkdouble":"194284"},{"date":"01:43 12/08","title":"Morata: \"Chelsea v\u1eeba chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/12/morata-chelsea-vua-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-cau-thu-dang-cap-the-gioi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Alvaro Morata ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Mateo Kovacic, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh The Blues \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1edf \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea m\u01b0\u1ee3n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Kovacic</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/mateo-kovacic-chinh-thuc-ra-mat-chelsea-172-194117.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 m\u01b0\u1ee3n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Mateo Kovacic</span> t\u1eeb Real Madrid, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i cho The Blues theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 1 n\u0103m. H\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t, b\u1edfi v\u1eady d\u00f9 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t hay d\u1edf th\u00ec v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a 2018/19 anh c\u0169ng s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Bernabeu.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alvaro Morata ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Mateo Kovacic h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Alvaro Morata ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Mateo Kovacic h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/Alvaro-Morata-phat-bieu-ve-Mateo-Kovacic-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea m\u01b0\u1ee3n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Kovacic\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKovacic \u0111\u1ebfn Chelsea nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n trong th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn c\u1ee7a th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Courtois c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Real Madrid. D\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Stamford Bridge theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n 1 n\u0103m, song c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i v\u1eabn quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cChelsea l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn \u1edf Anh, t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y. T\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t trong qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Chelsea, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf h\u1ebft kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng hy v\u1ecdng gi\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi tri\u1ebft l\u00fd b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a HLV Sarri, t\u00f4i \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng th\u00edch \u1ee9ng nhanh nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3. T\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Morata \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao Kovacic</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Alvaro Morata ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Mateo Kovacic, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh The Blues \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1edf \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Morata khen ngoi Kovacic\" title=\"Morata khen ng\u1ee3i Kovacic\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/12/morata-chelsea-vua-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-cau-thu-dang-cap-the-gioi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Morata khen ng\u1ee3i Kovacic</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u00f3 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt, t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 nh\u00e3n quan t\u1ed1t, Kovacic c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 ghi b\u00e0n, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00e1ng n\u1ec3. V\u1edbi Kovacic, nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u b\u00f3ng h\u01a1n\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cKovacic l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho Chelsea, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Kovacic v\u00e0 bi\u1ebft c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. T\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng gi\u00fap c\u1eadu \u1ea5y h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp nhanh nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi Chelsea\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cKhi t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2y, t\u00f4i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1. Kovacic l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi, v\u00e0 t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n gi\u00fap c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. Hy v\u1ecdng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p t\u1ed1t \u1edf Chelsea\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2253","checkdouble":"194285"},{"date":"00:57 12/08","title":"3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn Huddersfield 0-3 Chelsea","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/12/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-huddersfield-03-chelsea.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Huddersfield v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 3-0, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua danh s\u00e1ch 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn Huddersfield vs Chelsea v\u00f2ng 1 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: N'Golo Kante</h2>\r\n<div><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a HLV Maurizio Sarri v\u00e0 t\u00e2n binh Jorginho, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 N'Golo Kante \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p \u0111\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a anh d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Conte. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea9y l\u00ean \u0111\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kante ghi ban cho Chelsea\" title=\"Kante ghi b\u00e0n cho Chelsea\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/12/kante.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Kante ghi b\u00e0n cho Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kante l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1edbp c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0 s\u00fat xa t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i t\u1ed1t, song anh kh\u00f4ng ph\u00e1t huy \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng n\u00e0y khi ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1 qu\u00e1 th\u1ea5p. Khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i cao h\u01a1n, Kante \u0111\u00e3 ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Huddersfield trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5&nbsp; v\u00f2ng 1 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19, l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a The Blues nh\u01b0 v\u1ea5p ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong ho\u00e0n c\u1ea3nh nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, Kante \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd gi\u00fap Chelsea v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Ph\u00fat 34, t\u1eeb pha t\u1ea1t b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Willian, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p tung c\u00fa volley hi\u1ec3m h\u00f3c khi\u1ebfn th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Ben Hamer ch\u1ec9 bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ee9ng nh\u00ecn. B\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00fap Chelsea gi\u1ea3i t\u1ecfa \u00e1p l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 t\u00e2m l\u00fd v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u00eam 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u1eefa \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-0.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, Kante \u0111\u1ec1u ra s\u00e2n \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 34 tr\u1eadn/m\u00f9a nh\u01b0ng m\u1ed7i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i anh ch\u1ec9 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c duy nh\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i cao h\u01a1n, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: Alvaro Morata</h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">3 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Alvaro Morata \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh, nh\u01b0ng anh kh\u00f4ng ghi b\u00e0n c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o. HLV Sarri \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c ghi b\u00e0n, nh\u01b0ng nh\u1eefng g\u00ec Morata \u0111\u00e1p l\u1ea1i ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Morata tiep tuc gay that vong\" title=\"Morata ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/12/morata.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Morata ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Sarri v\u1eabn t\u1ecf ra ki\u00ean nh\u1eabn v\u1edbi Morata: &ldquo;C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111ang g\u1eb7p m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1ec1 t\u00e2m l\u00fd, t\u00f4i tin khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c kh\u1edfi tranh c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n&rdquo;.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Alvaro Morata \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed m\u0169i nh\u1ecdn trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Huddersfield, anh ch\u01a1i b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Willian v\u00e0 Pedro tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng. D\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Sarri tin t\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u01b0ng m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa Morata l\u1ea1i g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nD\u00f9 \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n 90 ph\u00fat nh\u01b0ng ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 n\u1ed5i m\u1ed9t c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch, anh ch\u1ec9 tung ra 2 pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00f4ng tr\u00fang khung th\u00e0nh. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea1o ra c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00e0o cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ed3i, ch\u1ecdn v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u00e0 tranh ch\u1ea5p k\u00e9m, Morata \u0111ang cho th\u1ea5y anh kh\u00f4ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng nhanh ch\u00f3ng l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i phong \u0111\u1ed9, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c v\u00e0o tay Giroud ho\u1eb7c th\u1eadm ch\u00ed b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y \u0111i v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1 t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Jorginho</h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Jorginho \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ra m\u1eaft Chelsea \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n v\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 27 tu\u1ed5i ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t trong vai tr\u00f2 \u0111\u00e1nh ch\u1eb7n, anh v\u00e0 Kante khi\u1ebfn h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng Huddersfield g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn khung th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Kepa.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jorginho co man ra mat NHM rat an tuong\" title=\"Jorginho c\u00f3 m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft NHM r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/12/jofrinho.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Jorginho c\u00f3 m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft NHA r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00e2n binh tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 57 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n 2 c\u00fa t\u1eafc b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 5 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1nh ch\u1eb7n, anh th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 66 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng 94%. Trong s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a Chelsea, Jorginho l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c cao nh\u1ea5t.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7, Jorginho c\u00f2n l\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t trong 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u00e0 Chelsea c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. Marcos Alonso mang v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 11m v\u00e0 HLV Sarri \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t, Jorginho b\u00ecnh t\u0129nh \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ghi t\u00ean m\u00ecnh l\u00ean b\u1ea3ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1. Ng\u00f4i sao 27 tu\u1ed5i l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 th\u1ee9 8 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u1eeb ch\u1ea5m 11m trong tr\u1eadn ra m\u1eaft t\u1ea1i Premier League, sau Brian Deane, Alan Thompson, Fabrizio Ravanelli, Peter Kennedy, Adam Le Fondre,&nbsp;Roberto Soldado v\u00e0 Alexandre Pato.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 \u0111\u00e1nh ch\u1eb7n v\u00e0 mang v\u1ec1 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, Jorginho \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ngo\u00e0i s\u1ee9c t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: Ross Barkley</h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ross Barkley \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 cao nh\u1ea5t n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Huddersfield vs Chelsea v\u00f2ng 1 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia mu\u1ed1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u n\u1ed1i gi\u1eefa h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o, song r\u1ea5t ti\u1ebfc c\u1ef1u sao Everton \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh t\u1ed1t nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ross Barkley co mot tran dau that vong\" title=\"Ross Barkley c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/12/barker.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ross Barkley c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t, anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng, Barkley c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng cho th\u1ea5y kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u00fat xa c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n anh ch\u1ec9 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m 1 l\u1ea7n, t\u1ea1o ra 1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u1ef1u sao Everton th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n, HLV Sarri \u0111\u00e3 r\u00fat anh ra ngh\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o Ruben Loftus-Cheek \u1edf ph\u00fat 68. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng t\u1ed1t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, Barkley c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u00e0o tay Loftus-Cheek, Mateo Kovacic ho\u1eb7c Cesc Fabregas.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Terence Kongolo</h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong 30 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Chelsea g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Huddersfield t\u1ea1o ra. Terence Kongolo l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Terence Kongolo xung dang nhan duoc nhung loi khen ngoi\" title=\"Terence Kongolo x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/12/kologo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Terence Kongolo x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div>C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh m\u00e0 c\u00f2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng b\u00f3ng b\u1ed5ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Chelsea th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec1u b\u1ecb Terence Kongolo ph\u00e1 ra, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1994 \u0111\u00e3 chia c\u1eaft r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t b\u1ed9 ba t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a The Blues.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea c\u1ee7a Terence Kongolo l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, anh c\u00f3 4 l\u1ea7n t\u1eafc b\u00f3ng, 6 l\u1ea7n ph\u00e1 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 4 l\u1ea7n kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. D\u00f9 Huddersfield th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i, anh c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Chelsea</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div>Khi m\u00e0 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/ha-guc-hudderfield-tan-hlv-sarri-danh-loi-khen-cho-mot-cai-ten-172-194283.html\" target=\"_blank\">Eden Hazard kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh</span>, nh\u1eefng t\u01b0\u1edfng sao tr\u1ebb Callum Hudson-Odoi s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh. Tuy nhi\u00ean, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 17 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Sarri tin t\u01b0\u1edfng, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Pero v\u00e0 Willian thay v\u00ec \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o Callum Hudson-Odoi.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nhung sao tre cua Chelsea khong co co hoi the hien minh\" title=\"Nh\u1eefng sao tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Chelsea kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n m\u00ecnh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/12/odoi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eefng sao tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Chelsea kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n m\u00ecnh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Khi m\u00e0 nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 58 tu\u1ed5i t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i Hazard v\u00e0 Victor Moses l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i Hudson-Odoi, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 17 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i Hudson-Odoi, m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a Chelsea nh\u01b0 Ethan Ampadu hay Tammy Abraham c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Sarri v\u1eabn c\u00f2n \u0111\u00f3 Gary Cahill v\u00e0 Andreas Christensen, b\u1edfi v\u1eady c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 Ampadu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u. Tammy Abraham c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn th\u1ee9 3 \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung phong sau Morata v\u00e0 Giroud.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2252","checkdouble":"194286"},{"date":"13:41 11/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Fulham vs Crystal Palace 21h00 ng\u00e0y 11/8 (Premier League 2018/19)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/nhan-dinh-fulham-vs-crystal-palace-21h00-ngay-118-premier-league-201819.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Fulham vs Crystal Palace l\u00fac 21h00 ng\u00e0y 11/8 (V\u00f2ng 1 gi\u1ea3i Premier League Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh NHA 2018/19): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Fulham vs Crystal Palace 21h00 ng\u00e0y 118 Premier League h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Fulham vs Crystal Palace 21h00 ng\u00e0y 118 Premier League h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/Fulham-vs-Crystal-Palace.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Fulham vs Crystal Palace</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span>Fulham vs Crystal Palace: 2-1<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>Sau 4 m\u00f9a ch\u01a1i \u1edf Championship, cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng Fulham c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng cao nh\u1ea5t x\u1ee9 s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9 Premier League. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Craven Cottage v\u1eabn gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed9 khung \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap h\u1ecd th\u0103ng h\u1ea1ng. Ngo\u00e0i ra th\u00ec Fulham c\u00f2n c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng Schurrle (t\u1eebng kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Chelsea) t\u1eeb Dortmund hay Vietto t\u1eeb Atletico Madrid, Chambers t\u1eeb Arsenal.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u00ean ph\u00eda Crystal Palace, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5t \u0111i nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 ch\u1ee7 ch\u1ed1t \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 n\u00e0o m\u00e0 c\u00f2n b\u1ed5 sung \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Jordan Ayew, Meyer. D\u1eabu v\u1eady th\u00ec s\u1ed1 t\u00e2n binh n\u00e0y c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. X\u00e9t v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng quan l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, d\u00f9 m\u1edbi th\u0103ng h\u1ea1ng nh\u01b0ng Fulham t\u1ecf ra kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 thua k\u00e9m Crystal Palace.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u00ecn v\u00e0o phong \u0111\u1ed9, Crystal Palace th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n giao h\u1eefu m\u00f9a h\u00e8 v\u1eeba qua: th\u1eafng 4/5 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Fulham ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2/8 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu h\u00e8.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy v\u1eady, giao h\u1eefu kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd l\u00e0 th\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111o ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c cho s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a 1 CLB b\u1edfi c\u00e1c HLV th\u01b0\u1eddng \u01b0u ti\u00ean th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m t\u00e2n binh c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt \u1edf c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu. Th\u00eam v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, Fulham ch\u1eb3ng h\u1ec1 e ng\u1ea1i Crystal Palace \u1edf s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Craven Cottage. T\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y Fulham c\u00f3 2 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 2 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a trong 4 cu\u1ed9c ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTin r\u1eb1ng Fulham s\u1ebd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 kh\u1ea3 quan trong ng\u00e0y m\u1edf m\u00e0n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00c0NH T\u00cdCH \u0110\u1ed0I \u0110\u1ea6U<br>\r\n2 \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 43 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, Fulham th\u1eafng 17 tr\u1eadn c\u00f2n Crystal Palace th\u1eafng 11 tr\u1eadn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00d4NG TIN L\u1ef0C L\u01af\u1ee2NG<br>\r\nFulham: Mawson, Tim Ream v\u00e0 Ayite ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u00f2n Denis Odoi b\u1ecb treo gi\u00f2.<br>\r\nCrystal Palace: Scott Dann ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng tham d\u1ef1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Meyer c\u00f2n b\u1ecf ng\u1ecf.</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2251","checkdouble":"194255"},{"date":"14:54 11/08","title":"T\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester, Pogba l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/mourinho-len-tieng-khi-pogba-va-sanchez-tranh-nhau-penalty.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Paul Pogba \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa MU v\u00e0 Leicester v\u1eeba qua. V\u00e0 sau tr\u1eadn, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 ghi d\u1ea5u m\u1ed9t k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c v\u1edbi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>Pogba t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"T\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester, Pogba l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"T\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester, Pogba l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/mourinho-len-tieng-khi-pogba-va-sanchez-tranh-nhau-penalty.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Pogba l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Leicester</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Pogba v\u1eabn \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea1t phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao sau khi gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u0103ng quang t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. V\u00e0 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/thong-tin-cau-thu/paul-pogba-44584.html\" target=\"_blank\">Paul Pogba</span> cho th\u1ea5y anh kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi khi \u0111\u00e3 l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t trong tr\u1eadn khai m\u1ea1c Premier League v\u1edbi Leicester v\u1eeba qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u1ec9 m\u1ea5t 2 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u, Pogba \u0111\u00e3 \u0111em v\u1ec1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf. Anh th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 11m d\u00f9 Schmeichel \u0111\u00e3 \u0111o\u00e1n \u0111\u00fang h\u01b0\u1edbng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng ph\u00fat sau \u0111\u00f3, Man United ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u00f9i l\u1ea1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. V\u00e0 \u0111\u1ebfn ph\u00fat 83, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng k\u1ebft li\u1ec5u tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u khi Luke Shaw ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p. Vardy g\u1ee1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 b\u00e0n cho Leicester ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd nh\u01b0ng ch\u1eebng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 \u201cb\u1ea7y c\u00e1o\u201d c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m.</div>\r\n<h2>Pogba l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Pogba qu\u1ea3 th\u1ef1c l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb th\u1ea7n may m\u1eafn v\u1edbi Man United. B\u1edfi m\u1ed7i khi anh l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u1ec1u gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng chung cu\u1ed9c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea, Pogba \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 11 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf Premier League. V\u00e0 Man United \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong c\u1ea3 11 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u00e0nh t\u00edch n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a Pogba ngang b\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Ryan Babel c\u1ee7a Liverpool trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 Lan c\u0169ng gi\u00fap The Kop gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 11 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong 11 tr\u1eadn m\u00e0 anh ghi b\u00e0n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay, Pogba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng v\u00e0 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Man United t\u1edbi th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u th\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u1ea1ng nh\u01b0 Premier League v\u00e0 Champions League. V\u00e0 n\u1ebfu ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean th\u00ec kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng l\u1edbn l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u MU 2-1 Leicester:</strong><br>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_278846\" style=\"width:100%;\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&vid=premierleague/2018/08/11/manutd-leicester-1533934869.mp4&autoplay=true\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" oallowfullscreen=\"\" msallowfullscreen=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"400\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c sau tr\u1eadn MU vs Leicester:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/4-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-mu-21-leicester-172-194247.html\">4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn MU 2-1 Leicester?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/mu-vs-leicester-tran-dau-vong-1-premier-league-201819-372-194203.html\">MU 2-1 Leicester: M\u00e0n kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u su\u00fdt ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o c\u1ee7a b\u1ea7y Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2250","checkdouble":"194256"},{"date":"15:03 11/08","title":"Emery quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m ch\u1eb7n \u0111\u1ee9ng m\u1ea1ch thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc Guardiola","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/10/emery-quyet-tam-chan-dung-mach-thua-truoc-guardiola.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha tr\u1ea5n an d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn sau khi hai ng\u00f4i sao l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh tranh nhau qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n trong tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng MU 2-1 Leicester \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1 Premier League 2018/19.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Paul Pogba cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u1ecbn v\u00e0 ch\u00ednh anh m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m \u1edf ngay ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 3. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p m\u1edbi \u0111\u0103ng quang ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup v\u00e0 gi\u1edd ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i cho Man Utd.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">N\u00f3i g\u00ec th\u00ec n\u00f3i, Alexis Sanchez c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i khi b\u1ecb tranh gi\u00e0nh nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t khi anh r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u m\u1edbi su\u00f4n s\u1ebb sau n\u1eeda n\u0103m kh\u1ed1n kh\u00f3 \u1edf Old Trafford. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, ch\u00ednh ng\u00f4i sao Chile \u0111\u00e3 \u0111em v\u1ec1 qu\u1ea3 penalty \u0111\u00f3 khi s\u00fat b\u00f3ng tr\u00fang tay h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Leicester trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Mourinho n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi Pogba v\u00e0 Sanchez tranh \u0111\u00e1 penalty h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Mourinho n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi Pogba v\u00e0 Sanchez tranh \u0111\u00e1 penalty h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/mourinho-len-tieng-khi-pogba-va-sanchez-tranh-nhau-penalty.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Pogba v\u00e0 Sanchez tranh \u0111\u00e1 penalty \u1edf tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng MU 2-1 Leicester</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, Pogba \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 v\u1ee5 v\u00e0 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 g\u00ec gi\u1eefa anh v\u00e0 Sanchez. C\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Juventus c\u00f3 n\u00f3i nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0y nh\u1eb1m tr\u1ea5n an d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn: <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh ri\u00eang m\u1ed9t ai \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec7m tr\u1ecdng tr\u00e1ch s\u00fat penalty c\u1ea3, k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 HLV c\u0169ng \u01b0u ti\u00ean ch\u00fang t\u00f4i t\u1ef1 d\u00e0n x\u1ebfp v\u1edbi nhau ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n can thi\u1ec7p. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ea7n t\u1edbi, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd nh\u01b0\u1eddng cho Alexis v\u00ec n\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi t\u00f4i, ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho Man Utd m\u00e0 th\u00f4i.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ti\u1ebfp l\u1eddi h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u01b0ng v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed3ng t\u00ecnh, HLV Jose Mourinho c\u0169ng l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng MU 2-1 Leicester \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1 Premier League 2018/19: \u201cPaul s\u00fat penalty r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 lu\u00f4n c\u00f3 t\u00e2m l\u00fd s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i v\u00e0 t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, t\u00f4i c\u00f3 c\u1ea3 s\u1ed1 hai v\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ba \u0111\u1ec1 ph\u00f2ng tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p thi\u1ebfu t\u1ef1 tin v\u00ec m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 l\u00fd do n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea5y.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201c\u0110\u1eebng qu\u00ean Paul gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi n\u00ean c\u1eadu \u1ea5y hi\u1ec3n nhi\u00ean r\u1ea5t t\u1ef1 tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ea5m 11m. Sau c\u00f9ng th\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u1eadu \u1ea5y t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n xuy\u00ean su\u1ed1t th\u1eddi gian di\u1ec5n ra World Cup 2018 c\u01a1 m\u00e0. Nh\u00ecn m\u00e0 xem, Kasper Schmeichel b\u1eaft ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc ra sao v\u00e0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u1eabn b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2249","checkdouble":"194257"},{"date":"15:22 11/08","title":"Klopp ph\u1ea5n kh\u1edfi khi Kepa ph\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a Alisson","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/10/klopp-phan-khoi-khi-kepa-pha-ky-luc-cua-alisson.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c cho r\u1eb1ng h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 t\u00e2n binh gi\u1edd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u0169 b\u1ecf \u00e1p l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">K\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 \u0111\u00f3ng c\u1eeda \u1edf Anh v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n, khi Kepa Arrizabalanga v\u00e0 Alisson Becker ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 hai b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t Premier League. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed ch\u1ec9 trong v\u00f2ng ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea7y m\u1ed9t th\u00e1ng, k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi trong khung g\u1ed7 \u0111\u00e3 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp b\u1ecb Liverpool v\u00e0 Chelsea ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1, t\u1eeb 67 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng l\u00ean 72 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Klopp vui Kepa ph\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a Alisson h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Klopp vui Kepa ph\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a Alisson h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/10/klopp-phan-khoi-khi-kepa-pha-ky-luc-cua-alisson.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Kepa ph\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a Alisson</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">V\u1ecb th\u1ebf c\u1ee7a Alisson ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c duy tr\u00ec trong th\u1eddi gian ng\u1eafn ng\u1ee7i nh\u01b0 v\u1eady nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi HLV Jurgen Klopp, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tin m\u1eebng cho h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 t\u00e2n binh c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng \u1edf Anfield. Theo \u0111\u00f3, ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t tuy\u1ec3n Brazil gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u0169 b\u1ecf \u00e1p l\u1ef1c n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1 t\u1eeb c\u00e1i m\u00e1c \u0111\u1eaft nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh sau khi \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb Kepa v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c: \u201cT\u00f4i c\u0169ng ngh\u0129 m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y di\u1ec5n ra theo chi\u1ec1u h\u01b0\u1edbng c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i cho Alisson, nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i \u00e1p l\u1ef1c v\u1eabn lu\u00f4n hi\u1ec7n h\u1eefu v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n. H\u1ecd bi\u1ebft \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 nh\u01b0ng c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 tin \u0111\u1ee9ng v\u1eefng, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 b\u1edfi ch\u00fang ta lu\u00f4n cho r\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u00f3, Alisson v\u00e0 Kepa kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Klopp nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t th\u00eam v\u1ec1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 bom t\u1ea5n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 qu\u1ed1c n\u1ed9i: \u201cChelsea \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 cho m\u00ecnh m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n tr\u1ebb trung v\u00e0 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc. V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 ti\u1ec1n b\u1ea1c \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng quan tr\u1ecdng b\u1edfi th\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi Bilbao l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3, ho\u1eb7c anh tr\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ee7 ti\u1ec1n ho\u1eb7c m\u1eddi anh \u0111i cho. D\u00f9 sao, th\u1eddi th\u1ebf c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i khi ch\u1ec9 \u00edt n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y th\u00f4i, kh\u00f4ng ai ngh\u0129 c\u00e1c th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c mua v\u1edbi c\u00e1i gi\u00e1 cao \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">V\u00f2ng 1 m\u1edf m\u00e0n Premier League 2017/18, Liverpool ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n West Ham tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Anfield trong khi Chelsea ph\u1ea3i h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a Huddersfield Town. Tuy nhi\u00ean, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng cao ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 Alisson m\u1edbi c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra m\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi c\u00f2n Kepa s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i th\u00eam \u00edt nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ebfn cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n sau.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/thu-mon-thong-tri-mua-chuyen-nhuong-he-2018-bon-thap-nien-binh-thuong-hoa-mot-tu-tuong-di-biet-172-194190.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/10/thu-mon-thong-tri-mua-chuyen-nhuong-he-2018-bon-thap-nien-binh-thuong-hoa-mot-tu-tuong-di-biet.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/thu-mon-thong-tri-mua-chuyen-nhuong-he-2018-bon-thap-nien-binh-thuong-hoa-mot-tu-tuong-di-biet-172-194190.html\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb m\u00f9a chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018: B\u1ed1n th\u1eadp ni\u00ean b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng h\u00f3a m\u1ed9t t\u01b0 t\u01b0\u1edfng d\u1ecb bi\u1ec7t</span><br>\r\nM\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018 ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp b\u1ecb x\u00f4 \u0111\u1ed5 \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n. Ch\u00ednh nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n Alisson v\u00e0 Kepa c\u0169ng l\u00e0 hai b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2248","checkdouble":"194258"},{"date":"14:39 11/08","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP Newcastle vs Tottenham 18h30 ng\u00e0y 11/8 (Premier League 2018/19)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/newcastle-vs-tottenham-ngoai-hang-anh-1182018.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Newcastle vs Tottenham: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng video clip k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Newcastle vs Tottenham gi\u1ea3i Premier League Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh NHA 2018/19 l\u00fac 18h30 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 11/8.</h2><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Newcastle vs Tottenham: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng video clip k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Newcastle vs Tottenham gi\u1ea3i Premier League Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh NHA 2018/19 l\u00fac 18h30 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 11/8.</h2></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2247","checkdouble":"194259"}]}